<p>BY&nbsp;<a href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/author/221658/laura-lajiness/">LAURA LAJINESS KAUPKE</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>&nbsp;SEP 30 2022, 8:06 PM EDT<img alt="a collage of spring 2023 shoe trends to know" src="https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/shoe-trends-index-1664561841.jpg?crop=0.295xw:0.590xh;0.0321xw,0.359xh&amp;resize=640:*"></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>With the change of season comes the urge to wear new things. In summer,&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g39545401/best-beach-cover-up-dresses/" rel="noreferrer noopener">breezy sundresses</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g8377/cute-swimsuits-for-women/" rel="noreferrer noopener">trendy swimsuits</a>. The<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g40899370/best-fall-boots/" rel="noreferrer noopener">&nbsp;best fall boots</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g38273044/best-everyday-coats/" rel="noreferrer noopener">coats</a>&nbsp;are kryptonite at the first signs of autumn. Come spring,&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g35247618/best-spring-jackets-for-women/" rel="noreferrer noopener">lightweight jackets</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g37665634/spring-2022-shoe-trends/" rel="noreferrer noopener">toe or ankle-baring shoes</a>&nbsp;are all you can think about after bundling in&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g41396917/best-puffer-jackets/" rel="noreferrer noopener">puffers</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g3124/best-snow-boots/" rel="noreferrer noopener">snow boots</a>. For those consistently looking ahead, the&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g37665634/spring-2022-shoe-trends/" rel="noreferrer noopener">best spring 2023 shoe trends</a>&nbsp;are proving to be c-h-i-c. But fret not: The&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g39766142/best-platform-sandals/" rel="noreferrer noopener">platforms</a>,&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g40912069/best-mary-janes/" rel="noreferrer noopener">Mary Janes</a>, and chunky&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g39002208/best-womens-loafers/" rel="noreferrer noopener">loafers</a>&nbsp;you're loving right now have a place in your next-season wardrobe, as do lovely&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g40315714/best-ballet-flats/" rel="noreferrer noopener">ballet flats</a>, though with a more literal&nbsp;<em>en pointe</em>&nbsp;twist.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>If you can't get enough&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g41042747/y2k-fashion/" rel="noreferrer noopener">Y2K fashion</a>,&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g35784892/amazon-prime-minimalist-fashion/" rel="noreferrer noopener">minimalist</a>&nbsp;silhouettes, including wider peep toe mules, are primed for dominance. And in place of your cold-weather&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g37976801/best-lug-sole-boots-women/" rel="noreferrer noopener">lug-sole boots</a>? Soaring chunky shapes, including flatforms, wedges (yes, really), and&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g7512/block-heel-sandals/" rel="noreferrer noopener">block heels</a>. Plus, cagey designs, including&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g40108770/best-fisherman-sandals/" rel="noreferrer noopener">fisherman sandals</a>&nbsp;and the delightfully whimsical return of&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/a9933457/you-ready-for-jellies/" rel="noreferrer noopener">jellies</a>. Keep scrolling for a deeper breakdown of the shoes set for cult status next season.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><em>Good Angle</em></p>
